    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has had an initial 15 min, add your <strong>meat-free sausages </strong>to the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to the oven for a further 25-30 min or until the veg is tender and the sausages are golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>sticky meat-free sausage, apple & root veg bake</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1617699568025-x200.jpg",
