            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the <strong>roasted garlic </strong>out of the skin into the bake, discard the skin and give it all a good mix up</p><p>Serve the <strong>sticky meat-free sausage, apple & root veg bake</strong>, discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves] </strong>and pour over any <strong>remaining juices</strong> from the tray[s]</p><p>Serve the<strong> balsamic salad</strong> to the side and sprinkle your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
